text: Map of Russia with Vladimir Oblast highlighted This is a list of rural localities in Vladimir Oblast. Vladimir Oblast (, Vladimirskaya oblast) is a federal subject of Russia (an oblast). Its administrative center is the city of Vladimir, which is located east of Moscow.
